otherFacts.name: Rooms
otherFacts.value: Bonus, Living Room, Kitchen, Dining Room

data.description: If you are looking for a furnished rustic country cabin in the mountains with acreage and a creek this one should be on the top of your list to see.  This cabin has a lot of character and a lot of possibilities. The location is perfect for someone who wants to have that private setting but the convenience of being right on a paved road.  This has a private well, room for RV parking, metal roof, rough cut  wood walls in the living area.  The main floor has two bedrooms, one full bath and laundry room.  On the 2nd floor you will find a bonus room with a 1/2 bath - perfect for guests or an office. There is just so much you can do to this one to make it your very own rustic cabin in the woods!
